## Nav menus

When you create a menu in **WP admin  Appearance  Menus**, you can select the location for that menu.

By default, the available locations are:

- Desktop menu
- Mobile menu
- User dashboard menu
- Create post menu

If you need to create more menu locations, you can register them in **WP admin  Voxel  Settings  Nav menus**

When registering a menu, you have to provide a **Label** and a **Key**. Make sure the key is unique to avoid conflicts with other menu locations
